channel.title: Change Wcing Speed
channel.description:
How Do I Speed Up/Slow Down A Magic Trees Wcing Speed. like logs per a minute and what not... i recently have been updating my server, and i added a magic tree, that gave 10m, 100k magic exp, and 100k wcing exp. but its slow cuttting the money. its like reguler magic tree cutting, if not slower. so how do i speed it up? i want the magic tree, to have the wcing speed of a normal tree. but i dont know how to change it. so if anyone could help me, that would be great,
-Will

item.title: Change Wcing Speed
item.dc:creator: @I_Br3ndan_I I Br3ndan I
item.description:
@I_Br3ndan_I wrote:

[code]case 5904:
return 25-lvlB;
//break;

case 1281:
case 3037:
return 35-lvlB;
//break;

case 1308:
case 5551:
case 5552:
case 5553:
return 45-lvlB;
//break;

case 1307:
case 4674:
return 60-lvlB;
//break;

case 1309:
return 85-lvlB;
//break;

case 1292:
case 1306:
return 36-lvlB;
//break;[/code]

There’s all the WC cases for the speed/timers. Change the numbers after ‘return’ to make it faster/slower. Higher the number the slower… Etc.
